%% DATA_MAINTENANCE Processing Sequence
sequenceDiagram
    participant MainLoop
    participant XFXCNTR
    participant XFXCYMD
    participant XFXLDSC
    participant XFXTABL

    MainLoop->>XFXCNTR: Evaluate BR 001 X equals zero
    XFXCNTR-->>MainLoop: Branch to EXIT when X equals zero

    MainLoop->>XFXCNTR: Evaluate BR 002 X equals 40
    XFXCNTR-->>MainLoop: Branch to EXIT when X equals 40

    MainLoop->>XFXCYMD: Evaluate BR 003 VYY < 1800
    XFXCYMD-->>MainLoop: EXIT when year before 1800

    MainLoop->>XFXCYMD: Evaluate BR 004 VYY > 2100
    XFXCYMD-->>MainLoop: EXIT when year after 2100

    MainLoop->>XFXCYMD: Evaluate BR 005 VMM < 01
    XFXCYMD-->>MainLoop: EXIT when month less than 01

    MainLoop->>XFXCYMD: Evaluate BR 006 VMM > 12
    XFXCYMD-->>MainLoop: EXIT when month greater than 12

    MainLoop->>XFXCYMD: Evaluate BR 008 VDD > DYS VMM
    XFXCYMD-->>MainLoop: EXIT when day beyond days in month

    MainLoop->>XFXLDSC: Evaluate BR 009 010 011 LDAMAP > 99
    XFXLDSC-->>MainLoop: EXIT when level map greater than 99

    MainLoop->>XFXLDSC: Evaluate BR 012 LDAMAP > 9999
    XFXLDSC-->>MainLoop: EXIT when level map greater than 9999

    MainLoop->>XFXTABL: Evaluate BR 013 014 015 016 IN79 on
    XFXTABL-->>MainLoop: EXIT when indicator 79 is on
